{
  "stem": "27687.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in, I stayed in Blechhammer till 1944 in winter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, Blechhammer, in Blechhammer, I, I was lucky again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the next day, they brought us to the workplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they divided electrician into groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who is electrician technician and who is electrician for building?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said I'm electrician technician.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they, there were a few people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They sent us to another group, to another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went there and all of a sudden, there came the buses, the big mechanics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of them was wearing a SS uniform with the death head on his cap and on his epaulettes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say to myself, I hope I'm not gonna get him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he marched around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, oh, you, come on out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, what can I do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he turned out to be the nicest man I've ever seen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He taught me electricity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he taught me everything possible for the trade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on top of that, he was the only one what had a key to a special part of the whole building, which was a powerhouse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that building, there was a part which filtered the smoke what goes out the smoke stacks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that the flyers what come, the American or the English, cannot see the smoke.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It filtered that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And inside, in that building, the electricity where the smoke goes through must have been at least two million volt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the plates with that load and electricity attracted the particles, the-- what goes out on the chimney and collects it in that, on the plates.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
